import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route, Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import AllMeetupsPage from './pages/AllMeetup'
import FavoritesPage from './pages/Favorites'

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/">
          <AllMeetupsPage />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/favorites">
          <FavoritesPage />
        </Route>
      </Routes>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
